lead_paragraph: England coach Trevor Bayliss knows there is no quick fix to his side's batting problems against spin but hopes that their recent exposure to conditions in Bangladesh will help them in a five-test series against India, starting next week.

headline.print_headline: No Quick Fix to England's Batting Woes, Says Coach Bayliss
